(h) knowingly does any act calculated to prejudice the maintenance of peace and good order in any area of rstriction;
(i) conceals or habours any person whom he knows or has reason to believe to be unlawfully outside any place or area which such person is, by or under these Regulations, prohibited from leaving or in which he is required to remain,
